Reasoning: The paper is about the MAVLink protocol used in unmanned systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the potential of MAVLink in enabling Internet connectivity, which relates to networking and communications (cs.NI). The security aspects of MAVLink are also discussed, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) and security and privacy (cs.CR). Finally, the paper provides a technical survey and tutorial on the MAVLink protocol, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
